race.description: Jgp We Stand With Tassie 5th Grade F
race.comment: ARMARTA (4) comes off a (19.46) win last time, scoring by 2 lengths in a Grade 5 over 366m at this track. Looks suited and should go close. BORN TO RACE (5) turned heads when clocking an exceptional 18.78 over 350m at Q Straight three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Must include on winning run three back. LOOKING FANCY (1) hit the ground running from out wide last start and crossed down to lead throughout (19.65) at this track in a Grade 5 over 366m. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to his name from five starts. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. ZIPPING HAGEN (2) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish.
